<%= render 'shared/header', title: 'Pricing' %>
<section class="wrapper">
  <div class="container pt-12 pb-[4.5rem] xl:pb-0 lg:pb-0 md:pb-0">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap mx-[-15px] lg:mx-[-20px] xl:mx-0 items-center">
      <!-- Text section (left) -->
      <div class="md:w-6/12 lg:w-6/12 xl:w-7/12 xxl:w-7/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] px-[15px] lg:px-[20px] xl:px-0 max-w-full xl:ml-4p">
        <div class="xl:!mt-10 lg:!mt-10 md:!mt-10 xl:!mb-20 lg:!mb-20 md:!mb-20 relative !z-10">
          <h2 class="text-[calc(1.305rem_+_0.66vw)] font-bold xl:text-[1.8rem] leading-[1.3] !mb-3">Pricing – No Surprises</h2>
          <div class="text-[1rem] leading-[1.7] font-medium">
            <p>We get it – you need to know if this fits your budget. The short answer? Our pricing starts at 700 EUR per month.</p>
            <p>But outbound isn’t a plug-and-play service. Some markets are harder to crack than others. Some businesses need a bigger push to stand out. That’s why we don’t do rigid pricing tiers – every campaign is built to match your specific goals, audience, and challenges.</p>
            <p>Our pricing is a combination of a fixed monthly fee and a percentage of deals closed. This ensures that we’re invested in real results – not just sending messages, but creating genuine opportunities that turn into revenue.</p>
            <p>But outbound isn’t a plug-and-play service. Some markets are harder to crack than others. Some businesses need a bigger push to stand out. That’s why we don’t do rigid pricing tiers – every campaign is built to match your specific goals, audience, and challenges.</p>
            <p>If 700 EUR sounds reasonable, let’s talk. We’ll walk you through the process, assess your market, and see if we’re the right fit to drive your growth.</p>
            <%= link_to "Let's discuss your budget <span class='arrow-container'>></span>".html_safe, "https://calendly.com/moocrew-intro/30min", target: "_blank", class: "btn btn-book !rounded-full !px-6 !py-2", aria: { label: "Let's discuss your budget" }, title: "Let's discuss your budget" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- /.content -->
      <!-- Image section (right) -->
      <div class="md:w-5/12 lg:w-5/12 xl:w-4/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] px-[15px] lg:px-[20px] xl:px-0 max-w-full xl:ml-4p sm:flex md:flex xl:!flex lg:!flex !relative">
        <%= image_tag("svg/doodle3.svg", class: "!h-[3rem] absolute hidden xl:block lg:block", style: "top: -20%; left: 20%", alt: "image") %>
        <figure class="relative z-[2]">
          <%= image_tag("exam.png", alt: "image", class: "w-full max-w-full !h-auto rounded-full") %>
        </figure>
      </div>
      <!--/column -->
    </div>
    <!--/column -->
  </div>
  <!--/.row -->
</div>
<!-- /.container -->
</section>
